Teach Greet using Name and Ending be "!"
  "{Name}{Ending}"

Teach Count Items using many Items
  Length of Items

Make Scores be Map with "Ada" meaning 10 and "Grace" meaning 12
Make Tags be Set with "ready" and "tested"
Make Ready Word be "ready"
Make Pair be Tuple with 7 and 8
Make First and Second be Pair
Make Add One be Teach using Number give Number plus 1

Say Use Greet with Name be "Ada" and Ending be "?"
Say Use Count Items with 1 and 2 and 3
Say "ready? {Ready Word is in Tags}"
Say First plus Second
Say Use Add One with 4

Make Count be 0
Repeat forever
  Change Count to Count plus 1
  If Count is less than 3
    Skip
  Stop
Say "loop {Count}"

Make Maybe Name be Some "Ada" as Maybe String
Match Maybe Name
  When Some Name
    Say "some {Name}"
  When nothing
    Say "none"

Match Count
  When Int named Amount
    Say "count {Amount}"
  When anything
    Say "other"

Make Trial be Success "ok"
Match Trial
  When Success Text
    Say Text
  When Failure Error
    Say Error

Try
  Make Needed be Need Failure "bad"
  Say Needed
Catch Error
  Say Error
Finally
  Say "finished"
